did.unittitle: National Girls and Women in Sports Day promotional broadside

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: Featuring SEC Champion team from 1981-1982 season with Head Coach Terry Hall; Assistant Coach Lynn Norenberg; Assistant Coach Dorothy Jean Berry; Trainer Mimi Porter; Manager Gary Loyd; and players Kathy Lokie, Valerie Still, Jody Runge, Grace Odrick, Terri Naiser, Tayna Fogle, Lisa Collins, Donna Martin, Patty Jo Hedges, Lori Edgington, Lea Wise, and Diane Stephens.
